    {
      "text": "Monster Rancher Battle Card GB, known in Japan as Monster Farm Battle Card GB (モンスターファームバトルカードGB, Monsutā Fāmu Batoru Kādo GB) is a strategy video game developed by Graphic Research and released in 1999 by Tecmo for the Game Boy Color. It is the first game in Tecmo's Monster Rancher Battle Card series, featuring a card game incorporating the popular characters from the Monster Rancher series. It was followed by a 2000 sequel Monster Rancher Battle Card Episode II for the PlayStation which featured additional monsters.",
